- Support provided to aid coordination, including through the Moldova Partnership Principles and its implementation plan, and support to the formulation and implementation of national development strategies and plans;
- UN Resident Coordinator's Office facilitates the UN Country Team's joint strategic planning and implementation through common programming tools, such as the UN Development Assistance Framework and instruments of Delivering as One UN;
- UN Resident Coordinator's Office provides support to the implementation of the Millennium Declaration and similar internationally agreed development goals.
